  "Matzah and Hamantashen Fan ✡️",
  "5x Magento Certified 🏅",
  "Problem Solver 🧠",
  "Torah Follower 🕎",
  "eCommerce Specialist 🛒",
  "Tea Guy 🍵",
  "Pythonista 🐍",
  "Idea Generator 💡",
  "Scooter Driver 🛴",
  "Software Engineer 👨‍💻",
  "Life Explorer 🧗‍♂️",
  "Science Learner 🚀",
  "Rookie Hacker 🔐",
  "Lifelong Student 📚",
  "AI Evangelist 🔮",
